              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052452/Encyclopedie van muziekinstrumenten (1977)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>泛指有雙簧與圓錐形內徑的簧管樂器。也可專指西方管弦樂團、室內樂跟獨奏樂中使用的雙簧簧管樂器。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use geralmente para tubos de junco com palheta dupla e furo cônico. Também pode ser usado especificamente para tubos de reedição com palheta dupla tocados em orquestra ocidental, câmara e música solo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109633/CVAA-BR Consortium (2020-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Allgemein verwendet für das Holzblasinstrument mit Doppelrohrblatt und konischer Röhre. Kann auch spezifischer für das Doppelrohrblattinstrument benutzt werden, das in westlicher Orchestermusik, Kammermusik oder für Soloaufführungen eingesetzt wird.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
